    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/e4585e268e62c62d42f47872326ef554.poster.avif?t=1762785797\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/e4585e268e62c62d42f47872326ef554.webm?t=1762785797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/e4585e268e62c62d42f47872326ef554.mp4?t=1762785797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>深入体验令人兴奋的汽车破碎模拟器，多样化的级别等你挑战。每个竞技场都提供新的汽车堆供你拆除。定制跳台高度和速度以实现史诗般的碰撞，摧毁汽车堆，赚取金币升级你的竞技场。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/76069bf11fe0d1df61cc96846264868b.poster.avif?t=1762785797\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/76069bf11fe0d1df61cc96846264868b.webm?t=1762785797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/76069bf11fe0d1df61cc96846264868b.mp4?t=1762785797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>解锁并从丰富的交通工具中进行选择，每辆都具有独特的物理特性，用你最喜欢的交通工具体验时尚碰撞带来的兴奋！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/aa528a09809337fb771302f722a7c3ae.poster.avif?t=1762785797\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/aa528a09809337fb771302f722a7c3ae.webm?t=1762785797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/aa528a09809337fb771302f722a7c3ae.mp4?t=1762785797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>赢得胜利的途径是碰撞，积累分数，沉浸在毁灭的刺激乐趣中。释放你内心的冒险家，享受这令人上瘾的混乱！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/8d851c82e40a192369dbce26321ea461.poster.avif?t=1762785797\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/8d851c82e40a192369dbce26321ea461.webm?t=1762785797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/8d851c82e40a192369dbce26321ea461.mp4?t=1762785797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>从丰富的酷炫汽车中进行选择，展开一场破坏狂潮<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/05a7b13080ffdedd3be413f639b2988e.poster.avif?t=1762785797\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/05a7b13080ffdedd3be413f639b2988e.webm?t=1762785797\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2367660/extras/05a7b13080ffdedd3be413f639b2988e.mp4?t=1762785797\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
